      </p></div><div><p><em><a title="Games > Freedom Wars Remastered [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/freedom-wars-remastered">Freedom Wars Remastered</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [8,618 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > PS4 [27,563 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [16,479 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [22,062 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> is the highlight of this week’s Japanese video game releases. <span id="more-936886"></span></p><p>Also due out this week is the Switch version of <em><a title="Games > The Fox's Way Home [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/the-foxs-way-home">The Fox’s Way Home</a></em>, the fishing <a title="Genres > RPG [16,902 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg">RPG</a> <em><a title="Games > Sea Fantasy [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/sea-fantasy">Sea Fantasy</a></em> for PC, and the console versions of <em><a title="Games > Boti: Byteland Overclocked [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/boti-byteland-overclocked">Boti: Byteland Overclocked</a></em>.</p><p>Get the full list of this week’s Japanese game releases below. It should be noted that <a title="Companies > Gematsu" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/gematsu">Gematsu</a> will receive a small percentage of money from purchases made through Play-Asia links. You can also save five percent with our multi-use “<strong>GEMATSU24</strong>” coupon code.</p><h2><span>Physical and Digital</span></h2><ul><li><em>Freedom Wars Remastered</em> (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/freedom-wars-remastered/13/70hpn3?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/freedom-wars-remastered/13/70hpn5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>) – Launching digitally worldwide.<ul><li>Asian Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/freedom-wars-remastered/13/70hpn7?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/freedom-wars-remastered/13/70hpn9?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li></ul><!-- AD: content -->
        </li></ul><h2><span>Digital-Only</span></h2><ul><li><em>Boti: Byteland Overclocked</em> (PS5, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [6,537 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, PS4, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [13,689 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>The Fox’s Way Home</em> (Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Freedom Wars Remastered</em> (PS4, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3004100/FREEDOM_WARS_Remastered/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Gravity Escape</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, Xbox One, Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Project Tower [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/project-tower">Project Tower</a></em> (PS5, PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2242970/Project_Tower/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>, <a href="https://store.epicgames.com/p/project-tower-010f57" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Epic Games Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em><a title="Games > Riven [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/riven">Riven</a>aar’s Grove</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, Xbox One, Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Sea Fantasy</em> (PC [<a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2835110/Sea_Fantasy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Sokocrab</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, Xbox One, PC [<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/sokocrab-windows/9n3602t694l4" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>]) – Launching worldwide.</li><li><em>Super Onion Boy+</em> (PS5, Xbox Series, PS4, Xbox One, Switch) – Launching worldwide.</li></ul><h2><span><strong>West</strong></span></h2><ul><li><em><a title="Games > Ys Memoire: The Oath in Felghana [12 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/ys-memoire-the-oath-in-felghana">Ys Memoire: The Oath in Felghana</a></em> (PS5, PS4, Switch) – PlayStation 4 version is digital-only.<ul><li>North American Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/ys-memoire-the-oath-in-felghana-refined-edition/13/70hexr?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/ys-memoire-the-oath-in-felghana-refined-edition/13/70hey1?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li><li>European Version (<a href="https://www.play-asia.com/ys-memoire-the-oath-in-felghana/13/70hgzl?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PS5</a>, <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/ys-memoire-the-oath-in-felghana/13/70hgzn?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Switch</a>)</li></ul></li></ul><p>The PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, and Switch titles listed above can be purchased through Japanese <a title="Platforms > PlayStation [46,699 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation">PlayStation</a> Network and <a title="Platforms > Nintendo [21,297 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo">Nintendo</a> accounts using prepaid cards:</p><ul><li>PlayStation Store cards (yen): <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-1100-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/70dc0b?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,100</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-3000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk5?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-5000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk4?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/psn-card-10000-yen-playstation-network-japan/13/703xk3?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10,000</a></li><li>Nintendo eShop cards (yen): <a href="https://www.play-asia.com/nintendo-eshop-card-1000-yen-japan-account/13/704a2v?tagid=578221" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">1,000</a> / <a href="https://www.play-asi